ids-scratchjr.html\">PBS Kids APP<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Snap<\/span><em>!<\/em> (formerly BYOB) is a visual, drag-and-drop programming language. It is an extended reimplementation of <a href=\"https:\/\/scratch.mit.edu\/\">Scratch<\/a> that allows you to Build Your Own Blocks. It also features first class\u00a0lists, first class procedures, and continuations. These added capabilities make it suitable for a serious introduction to computer science for high school or college students.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Scratch Conference August 2016, Boston. It was a great honour to have out proposal accepted for the 2016 Scratch Conference at MIT. Not only to share out work with other educators from around the world but to meet and connect&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[52,72,46],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1462"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1462"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1462\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1469,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1462\/revisions\/1469"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1462"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/www.readysaltedcode.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1462"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag